
Instructions:

Start with example2
1) Add two hpx addreses to the Domain structure:  complete 
2) In mainAction, declare a new LCO:  complete
3) Pass the new LCO complete to initDomain and assign it to the Domain structure
4) Add a new action, called advanceDomain
5) Create an unsigned long called epoch, set it to zero.
6) Using hpx_call, call advanceDomain for  [0,nDoms).  Pass it the global address space for domain as well as
the epoch variable.
7) In advanceDomain, access the Domain and set the complete LCO.  
